items.name: Technical Crafting Table
items.description:
This is the custom crafting table for tekPack.
 Every recipe in blue needs to be crafted in here.

items.name: tekBook
items.description: You get this item at the start of your journey. It guides you through the different concepts and recipes and shows necessary information with images and custom fonts.

items.name: Cable
items.description:
Connect your machines and devices with cables to power everything. 
Capacity: 1 EP(Energy Point)
Speed: 1 EP / 100ms

items.name: Battery Cell
items.description:
A thing that indicates energy storage.
 Primarily used for further crafting and upgrades.

items.name: Battery
items.description:
Stores Energy and displays it.(blue input, red output)
 Default Capacity: 15 EP.
 Can be deactivated by redstone.
Battery Cells can be inserted to upgrade the capacity(each 5 EP)

items.name: Generator
items.description:
Turns fuel into electric energy.
 1 Burn Point -> 1 EP (e.g coal -> 8 EP)
Stores up to 15 EP internally

items.name: Solar Panel
items.description:
Alternative energy producer.
 Generates EPs based on the light insolation(doesn't work at night).
Can provide up to 1 EP / 10s

items.name: Wind Turbine
items.description:
Generates power based on the height difference. The more height from the ground -> more energy.
Stacked on top of each other passes energy in the lowest turbine.
Has cool animations.
Can generate up to 1 EP/ 7s

items.name: Water Turbine
items.description:
Generates power based on falling water in front of it. The more height to the water source -> more energy.
Has cool animations.
Can generate up to 1 EP/ 7s

items.name: Turbine Blades
items.description: Just used to craft any turbines.

items.name: Electric Furnace
items.description:
Melts items like a normal furnace but with energy.
 Shows if energy is available.
1 EP -> 1 Item

items.name: Block Breaker
items.description:
Isn't it obvious?
 It breaks blocks in front of it(not unbreakable, ungrown plants) using energy(5 EP / block break, stores 15)
Can automate many things. Deactivated by redstone.

items.name: Vacuum Hopper
items.description:
Sucks all items in a radius of 4 blocks in.
 Pretty expensive.
 Uses 1 EP per Item(15 EP storage)
Can be deactivated by redstone.

items.name: Drill
items.description:
When powered digs a 5x5 hole till a undestroyable block and mines ores stuff.
 Everthing is transported upwards by a tube and dropped in front of it.
Mines a block every 2s for 1 EP / 2 EP for new stage(15 internal storage)

items.name: Conveyor Belt
items.description:
Transports all kind of entities in the pointed direction.
 Great for transporting items.

items.name: Extractor
items.description: Can extract items out of a item container and puts them as entities on a conveyor belt.

items.name: Item Filter
items.description:
When placed inside a hopper it filters the item that is in the first slot.
 A extractor has to face the hopper.
